## V2 Monitoring Metrics Droplet Filesystem Free [/v2/monitoring/metrics/droplet/filesystem_free{?host_id,start,end}]

### monitoringgetdropletFilesystemFreeMetrics [GET]
To retrieve filesystem free metrics for a given droplet, send a GET request to `/v2/monitoring/metrics/droplet/filesystem_free`.
+ Parameters
