## V2 Customers My Balance Response (object)


### Properties
+ `account_balance`: `12.23` (string, optional) - Current balance of the customer's most recent billing activity.  Does not reflect `month_to_date_usage`.
+ `generated_at`: `2019-07-09T15:01:12Z` (string, optional) - The time at which balances were most recently generated.
+ `month_to_date_balance`: `23.44` (string, optional) - Balance as of the `generated_at` time.  This value includes the `account_balance` and `month_to_date_usage`.
+ `month_to_date_usage`: `11.21` (string, optional) - Amount used in the current billing period as of the `generated_at` time.


## V2 Customers My Billing History Response (object)


### Properties
+ `billing_history` (array[BillingHistory], optional) 
+ `links` (Links, optional) 
+ `meta` (Meta1, required) - Information about the response itself.


## BillingHistory (object)


### Properties
+ `amount`: `12.34` (string, optional) - Amount of the billing history entry.
+ `date`: `2018-06-01T08:44:38Z` (string, optional) - Time the billing history entry occurred.
+ `description`: `Invoice for May 2018` (string, optional) - Description of the billing history entry.
+ `invoice_id`: `123` (string, optional) - ID of the invoice associated with the billing history entry, if  applicable.
+ `invoice_uuid`: `example-uuid` (string, optional) - UUID of the invoice associated with the billing history entry, if  applicable.
+ `type` (enum[string], optional) - Type of billing history entry.
    + `ACHFailure`
    + `Adjustment`
    + `AttemptFailed`
    + `Chargeback`
    + `Credit`
    + `CreditExpiration`
    + `Invoice`
    + `Payment`
    + `Refund`
    + `Reversal`


## Meta1 (object)
Information about the response itself.

### Properties
+ `total`: `1` (number, optional) - Number of objects returned by the request.


