+ `id`: `e78247f8-b1bb-4f7a-8db9-2a5f8d4b8f8f` (string, optional) - A unique ID that can be used to identify and reference the node.
+ `name`: `adoring-newton-3niq` (string, optional) - An automatically generated, human-readable name for the node.
